_meanings:
{@--1@}
To deserve, merit, be worthy of
(with <ab>acc.</ab> or <ab>inf.</ab>); {#kimiva#} 
{#nAyuzmAnamareSvarAnnArhati#} <ls>Ś. 7</ls>; so {#daMqaM, prAyaScittaM#},
{#vaDaM#} &c.

{@--2@} To have a right to, be
entitled to, be allowed to do any
thing (with <ab>acc.</ab>); {#nanu garBaH pitryaM#} 
{#rikTamarhati#} <ls>Ś. 6</ls>; {#na strI svAtaMtryamarhati#}  
<ls>Ms. 9. 3</ls>; also with <ab>inf.</ab>; {#na sa#} 
{#tallabDumarhati#} <ls>Ms. 8. 147</ls>; <ls n="Ms.">11. 7</ls>, <ls n="Ms. 11.">18.</ls>

{@--3@} To
be obliged or required to do a thing,
<ab>oft.</ab> implying duty or obligation;
{#nAnyatstrI dAtumarhati#} <ls>Y. 2. 49</ls>; {#imAM#} 
{#prasAdayitumarhasi#} <ls>R. 1. 88.</ls>

{@--4@} To be fit or
deserve to be done; {#arTanA mayi#} 
{#BavadBiH kartumarhati#} <ls>N. 5. 112</ls>; <ls>Dk. 137.</ls>

{@--5@}
To be equal to; be worth, {#na te#} 
{#gAtrARyupacAramarhaMti#} <ls>Ś. 3. 18</ls> are not
equal to; {#sarve te japayajYasya kalAM#} 
{#nArhaMti zoqaSIM#} <ls>Ms. 2. 86</ls>; <ls n="Ms.">3. 131.</ls>

{@--6@}
To be able, translateable by ‘can’;
{#na me vacanamanyaTA Bavitumarhati#} <ls>Ś. 4</ls>;  
{#vinASamavyayasyAsya na kaScitkartumarhati#}  
<ls>Bg. 2. 17</ls>; {#anudyogena tElAni tileByo#} 
{#nAptumarhati#} <ls>H. Pr. 30</ls> cannot get.

{@--8@} (Used with <ab>inf.</ab> in the second
<ab>pers.</ab> and sometimes in the third)
{#arh#} represents a mild form of 
command, advice or courteous request,
and may be translated by ‘pray’,
‘deign’, ‘be pleased to’, ‘will be 
pleased to’; {#dvitrARyahAnyarhasi soQumarhan#}  
<ls>R. 5. 25</ls> pray wait &c; {#nArhasi me praRayaM#}
{#vihaMtuM#} <ls n="R.">2. 58</ls>; {#taM saMtaH SrotumarhaMti#} <ls n="R.">1. 10</ls>
will be pleased or be good enough
to listen to it; <ls>Ku. 6. 32</ls>;  
<ls>Ms. 1. 2</ls>; <ls>Bg. 10. 16</ls>, <ls n="Bg.">2. 17</ls>; <ls>R. 1. 72</ls>; <ls n="R.">1. 88</ls>; 

<ls n="R.">3. 46.</ls>

or {c10c} <ab>P.</ab> To honour,
worship; {#rAjArjihattaM maDuparkapARiH#}  
<ls>Bk. 1. 17</ls>; <ls>Ms. 3. 3</ls>, <ls n="Ms. 3.">119.</ls>
